cs.RO, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.MA 

This paper is primarily focused on the design and analysis of metamorphic robotic systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). However, the paper also utilizes ideas from geometric group theory (cs.GT) and presents an algorithm for optimizing reconfiguration sequences, which involves concepts from control systems (cs.SY), dynamical systems (cs.DS), and mathematical optimization (cs.MA).
